The orientation of the basal component on the moment on the plane ab is undetermined, and has been chosen along a direction that maximizes the symmetry.
Modulus of the magnetic moment forced equal on the three sites: 0.7
cubic setting with origin choice 1
Later (J. Phys.: Condens. Matter 20 (2008) 104238), a structural phase transition has been reported  to happen simultaneously with the magnetic ordering, with a different propagation vector, which refutes this model.
