_active_magnetic_irreps_details
;
3k magnetic structure
The model includes correlations among the spins of the three independent sites that are not symmetry forced.
Superposition of two irreps acting as primary (mX2 with k=(0,0,1) and mX4 for k=(0,1,0) and (1,0,0). The model also correlates the amplitudes of the two irreps.
Not clear if more simple models associated with a single active irrep for the three k-vectors have been tried.
